reviews: I ordered a black one and a brown , the size of these are totally different , the black one is loose and longer and the Brown one is really tight and smaller . You would think that " made in the USA " would have better consistency and quality assurance . Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

Amazing quality and looks great. Not to mention super warm. Working in the trades I have purchased thousands of dollars of Carhartt product and this, like the rest doesn’t disappoint. This toque definitely isn’t fitted to the head at the top- so heads up if that’s not your thing!

I’m a girl and I bought this hat thinking it may be a little large, however if anything it fits a bit snug. Haven’t washed it yet but I’m hoping it’ll stretch easier after a wash. Also it’s a little long so the top sticks up a bit but I like the style so no complaints

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

review_title: Fits my XL head! Finally a one size fits all that does!
reviews: Finally a hat that fits my XL head! When companies say one size fits all, they’re normally lying. This hat fits. Keeps my head fairly warm in the fall weather probably too light for the negative weather in Ontario.

I work outside during the winter and this hat is perfect. I have a big head and the hat is fairly big even for me. That being said it was exactly what I needed. Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.
Shopper Kricket

Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.
Shopper Kricket

I bought this for my boyfriend for Christmas as he uses the Carhart brand quite a bit for workwear. It is too “tall”. We do not like the oversized look, I was expecting this hat to be a smaller, proper fit. I’m disappointed because he hasn’t worn this hat since I bought it for him, and most likely won’t wear it due to it being too big. It’s a shame because it looks like a really nice hat until it’s put on.

I ordered a black one and a brown , the size of these are totally different , the black one is loose and longer and the Brown one is really tight and smaller . You would think that " made in the USA " would have better consistency and quality assurance . Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

Amazing quality and looks great. Not to mention super warm. Working in the trades I have purchased thousands of dollars of Carhartt product and this, like the rest doesn’t disappoint. This toque definitely isn’t fitted to the head at the top- so heads up if that’s not your thing!

I’m a girl and I bought this hat thinking it may be a little large, however if anything it fits a bit snug. Haven’t washed it yet but I’m hoping it’ll stretch easier after a wash. Also it’s a little long so the top sticks up a bit but I like the style so no complaints

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

review_title: Fits my XL head! Finally a one size fits all that does!
reviews: Finally a hat that fits my XL head! When companies say one size fits all, they’re normally lying. This hat fits. Keeps my head fairly warm in the fall weather probably too light for the negative weather in Ontario.

I work outside during the winter and this hat is perfect. I have a big head and the hat is fairly big even for me. That being said it was exactly what I needed. Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.
Shopper Kricket

I bought this for my boyfriend for Christmas as he uses the Carhart brand quite a bit for workwear. It is too “tall”. We do not like the oversized look, I was expecting this hat to be a smaller, proper fit. I’m disappointed because he hasn’t worn this hat since I bought it for him, and most likely won’t wear it due to it being too big. It’s a shame because it looks like a really nice hat until it’s put on.

I ordered a black one and a brown , the size of these are totally different , the black one is loose and longer and the Brown one is really tight and smaller . You would think that " made in the USA " would have better consistency and quality assurance . Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Amazing quality and looks great. Not to mention super warm. Working in the trades I have purchased thousands of dollars of Carhartt product and this, like the rest doesn’t disappoint. This toque definitely isn’t fitted to the head at the top- so heads up if that’s not your thing!

Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.
Shopper Kricket

I bought this for my boyfriend for Christmas as he uses the Carhart brand quite a bit for workwear. It is too “tall”. We do not like the oversized look, I was expecting this hat to be a smaller, proper fit. I’m disappointed because he hasn’t worn this hat since I bought it for him, and most likely won’t wear it due to it being too big. It’s a shame because it looks like a really nice hat until it’s put on.

I ordered a black one and a brown , the size of these are totally different , the black one is loose and longer and the Brown one is really tight and smaller . You would think that " made in the USA " would have better consistency and quality assurance . Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

Amazing quality and looks great. Not to mention super warm. Working in the trades I have purchased thousands of dollars of Carhartt product and this, like the rest doesn’t disappoint. This toque definitely isn’t fitted to the head at the top- so heads up if that’s not your thing!

I’m a girl and I bought this hat thinking it may be a little large, however if anything it fits a bit snug. Haven’t washed it yet but I’m hoping it’ll stretch easier after a wash. Also it’s a little long so the top sticks up a bit but I like the style so no complaints

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

review_title: Fits my XL head! Finally a one size fits all that does!
reviews: Finally a hat that fits my XL head! When companies say one size fits all, they’re normally lying. This hat fits. Keeps my head fairly warm in the fall weather probably too light for the negative weather in Ontario.

I work outside during the winter and this hat is perfect. I have a big head and the hat is fairly big even for me. That being said it was exactly what I needed. Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.
Shopper Kricket

I bought this for my boyfriend for Christmas as he uses the Carhart brand quite a bit for workwear. It is too “tall”. We do not like the oversized look, I was expecting this hat to be a smaller, proper fit. I’m disappointed because he hasn’t worn this hat since I bought it for him, and most likely won’t wear it due to it being too big. It’s a shame because it looks like a really nice hat until it’s put on.

I ordered a black one and a brown , the size of these are totally different , the black one is loose and longer and the Brown one is really tight and smaller . You would think that " made in the USA " would have better consistency and quality assurance . Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Amazing quality and looks great. Not to mention super warm. Working in the trades I have purchased thousands of dollars of Carhartt product and this, like the rest doesn’t disappoint. This toque definitely isn’t fitted to the head at the top- so heads up if that’s not your thing!

Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.
Shopper Kricket

I bought this for my boyfriend for Christmas as he uses the Carhart brand quite a bit for workwear. It is too “tall”. We do not like the oversized look, I was expecting this hat to be a smaller, proper fit. I’m disappointed because he hasn’t worn this hat since I bought it for him, and most likely won’t wear it due to it being too big. It’s a shame because it looks like a really nice hat until it’s put on.

I ordered a black one and a brown , the size of these are totally different , the black one is loose and longer and the Brown one is really tight and smaller . You would think that " made in the USA " would have better consistency and quality assurance . Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

Amazing quality and looks great. Not to mention super warm. Working in the trades I have purchased thousands of dollars of Carhartt product and this, like the rest doesn’t disappoint. This toque definitely isn’t fitted to the head at the top- so heads up if that’s not your thing!

I’m a girl and I bought this hat thinking it may be a little large, however if anything it fits a bit snug. Haven’t washed it yet but I’m hoping it’ll stretch easier after a wash. Also it’s a little long so the top sticks up a bit but I like the style so no complaints

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

review_title: Fits my XL head! Finally a one size fits all that does!
reviews: Finally a hat that fits my XL head! When companies say one size fits all, they’re normally lying. This hat fits. Keeps my head fairly warm in the fall weather probably too light for the negative weather in Ontario.

I work outside during the winter and this hat is perfect. I have a big head and the hat is fairly big even for me. That being said it was exactly what I needed. Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.
Shopper Kricket

I bought this for my boyfriend for Christmas as he uses the Carhart brand quite a bit for workwear. It is too “tall”. We do not like the oversized look, I was expecting this hat to be a smaller, proper fit. I’m disappointed because he hasn’t worn this hat since I bought it for him, and most likely won’t wear it due to it being too big. It’s a shame because it looks like a really nice hat until it’s put on.

I ordered a black one and a brown , the size of these are totally different , the black one is loose and longer and the Brown one is really tight and smaller . You would think that " made in the USA " would have better consistency and quality assurance . Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

Maybe these are fakes I don't know , but when it says " one size fits all " they must mean buy three different colors and maybe one of them will fit , because they will all be different . Or they sent me a little boys one and a men's , but they are both labeled the same .

The products arrived on time and did in fact have Made in Canada on them. I gave these as gifts and the feedback was overall very good. It is a one size fits all, but more importantly, the hats keep you warm and are easy to maintain. People have raised concern that the tags are false and this is made in China, however the quality feels strong on the Black Toques and have so far performed very good.

This product is exactly as described. It is a heavy, good quality material. There is very little give in this hat, and it keeps it's shape well. It is very easy to clean, and seems to not hold odors like other materials do. I have owned several of these hats in the past and will continue to purchase these in the future.

Overall: It is an awesome, warm hat and a great value too! I would definitely recommend these to anyone, and can't wait to give these out as gifts this holiday season.

Amazing quality and looks great. Not to mention super warm. Working in the trades I have purchased thousands of dollars of Carhartt product and this, like the rest doesn’t disappoint. This toque definitely isn’t fitted to the head at the top- so heads up if that’s not your thing!

I’m a girl and I bought this hat thinking it may be a little large, however if anything it fits a bit snug. Haven’t washed it yet but I’m hoping it’ll stretch easier after a wash. Also it’s a little long so the top sticks up a bit but I like the style so no complaints

Picture made it look like this one for on your head perfect, but this one leaves that awkward little extra bit of hat stick off the top of your head, I like the top of my head to hit the hat, it's like how some kids wear their hat above their ears so they have a bit sticking high up, it's just weird, fashionable I suppose.

It's also really tight, probably better if you're bald, if you have some hair, you'll get serious hat head.

review_title: Fits my XL head! Finally a one size fits all that does!
reviews: Finally a hat that fits my XL head! When companies say one size fits all, they’re normally lying. This hat fits. Keeps my head fairly warm in the fall weather probably too light for the negative weather in Ontario.

I work outside during the winter and this hat is perfect. I have a big head and the hat is fairly big even for me. That being said it was exactly what I needed. Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come

This toque!!! so well made tightly woven perfectly stitched Carhartt Logo. A staple for my winter/fall wardrobe Carhartt since 1889 I mean c'mon, definitely a reliable Brand.

You wont regret this buy.

It’s a shame because it looks like a really nice hat until it’s put on.

review_title: Holds up to washes. Great quality.
reviews: My biggest issue with toques is they often don't hold up well after being washed. This one is just as good after being washed. You really can't beat Carhartt for their quality at this price point. Excellent product.

I love this toque, I've worn it everywhere. I had to stretch it out over the headrest of my computer chair the first night I got it, but after that it's fit my big head great. This is not the "fashion" version of the toque but honestly I've found no difference in how it looks on your head. It's still nice and long so there's that empty space at the top of the head and it just looks really nice (plus it's warm!).
Fits greatly. Thick enough to keep your head warm. The only discomfort is that it is from acrylic, so some people might be sensitive to it. After all, I am very satisfied with my purchase.

16$ for a toque that is super well made and durable. I have a bunch of different colours. Another thing I love is they are MADE in Canada. Where can you find something of this quality for that price that is made at home? Great job Carhartt!
It's nice quality but its so long it sticks up way too much unless you fold it so much that it looks equally as ridiculous. it looks like something from a H3H3 video tbh

This is a repeat purchase for our house! These carhart hats are so warm and comfy! Nice stretch to them so fit a variety of head sizes. Love that they come in a variety of colors! These wear and wash so well!! Love them!

I ordered this for my boyfriend, however when I opened it I noticed immediately it is extremely stretched out. The photos display it to be a short toque style, however when I opened it the hat is very long and would not fit anybody’s head properly. I’m very disappointed as I was looking forward to this surprise for him.
Logo looked a little torn in the seems, thick ass Toque and fit was weird and bulky and over all masive Toque. Filed this under donations. "Yes I'm Canadian and said to Toque"

review_title: The Great Quality You Would Expect
reviews: I purchased the black hat and it came very quickly (same day), and the quality is fantastic. Very warm, not scratchy, no issues with the seam. I know some of the other reviews mentioned issues, possibly with where is was manufactured. The black hat was made in Canada and had all of the proper Carhart tags/labels.

Overall, this hat is warm. If it is -5 degrees Celcius or higher I don't wear my hood. If it is much colder than -5 degrees Celsius then the hat is not enough and I put my jacket's hood on. I think this hat will be fine all winter. I have not had any quality issues with it so far.

review_title: The best of the four I bought
reviews: I bought four toques at the same time, adding to several I already had. I like this one the best. It is the softest and has a gentle stretch so it never feels tight. It fits well. It is warm without becoming too hot. The black one I got is made in Canada and is the best quality of them all.
I lost this hat a few months ago but let me tell ya it was a damn good hat when I had it! Nice and warm and the had is even long enough to cover your ears so they dont freeze off!
This is a toque is great. I have purchased two , I have one at the house and one at work. You can purchase this knowing you are getting great quality from Carhartt

I hesitated because if hats are not tall enough they slip off my head. I was worried this wouldn't fit as well as the ones I've tried on but balked at the inflated prices. This is super cozy and comfy and cute. I doubt I'll take it off my head this winter as we Canadians start the hibernation process.

First of all, this is a warm hat. I would save this one for especially cold days. It also makes me feel like a rough n' tumble construction worker because of the Carhartt label on the front. :-) Recommended!

review_title: Warm but made for Sasquatch heads
reviews: Nice warm touque, good for Winnipeg weather! They have changed the fit on these a bit though since my last one, you get a bit of a “tip” on top of your head and I have a big Mellon....

I ordered a Carhartt hat off amazon and i liked it so much I decided to order 2 more colours. I got a black one and the marled navy one as a gift and they are both about an inch taller and half an inch wider than my other one so now these just fit stupid and I have a big head so I can’t imagine how it will look on the person I’m giving the navy one too. Very unhappy

My son loves these, along with the Carhartt coat and hat for the cold winter, especially working outdoors.
Solid brand. Highly recommend!!

Hard to see in photo but this hat is very long. I don't like extra hat hanging off my head, it looks ridiculous. I had to fold it over twice to make it fit nicer. Would rather have bought a different hat, but it gets the job done.

Cute! Fits great! Warm! Has the authentic tag. Only complaint is that it was that it came wrinkled in the centre, not sure if I can remedy with a steam or iron. Isn’t too noticeable since it’s black, but it’s a wrinkle/fold that shouldn’t be there and is “permanent”/“pressed in” so to speak.

review_title: A little small but overall good
reviews: I have another carhartt hat that i bought in store and boathouse recently and the one that i just bought from there fits a lot more comfy and just perfect. The one i ordered from here was really small on me and did not fit right, but overall other than that is great

fits well and keeps my head warm
Got electricians heated wearing carhart like nah i don't know how to fix your breaker but i look like i do

My teenage daughter loves these toques! Collecting all of the colour options, it would seem.
Well made and comfortable.
Not my first Carhartt beanie, however the fit of this one is horrendous. It's so so deep and puffy on top. Disappointed in the fit, was expecting the old fit, that was less elongated.
Love love love. Comfortable and keeps my head warm when I'm out doing yard work in any weather! Hubby loves to steal it for work too lol

review_title: Cheap quality hat thats great for anyone
reviews: Hat stretches to fit your head. Great product. Im an apprentice carpenter and it holds up very well on the job. Holds up for easily half a year for like $12? Lots of colors to choose for different days of the week too which I like. Can't be beat imo.
love it ! super comfy and affordable. arrived quickly and in great condition. would buy again !
Well made and thick. The fold is not stitched, it can be unfolded to cover ears. Highly recommend the product.
If you're gonna be basic, might as well get this hat because it looks great on literally everybody.

Its literally massive. I cant wear it comfortably without having an extra 4 or 5 inches of hat above my head it looks kinda stupid. the only hat ive ever worn that is too big and too small at the same time how is that even possible lol

review_title: The tallest hat I've ever owned.
reviews: The hat is warm, well built. The stitching on the logo badge is good. But the hat is SO TALL. If it wasn't for the logo, I would double up on the brim roll. Rather, I'm left looking like I just raided Ethan Klein's hat collection. It's almost comical how tall this hat is.

I don't know if this has been mentioned before but this hat feels really itchy in me! Like I can't wear it straight for more than 3-4hours or I start scratching my forehead like crazy. Someone please tell me how I can make my hat less itchy... Other than that, it's a nice hat
My husband really likes this hat and has already worn it. It’s quite soft and well made! Love that.
simple, durable, and fit very well. I saw a lot of people wearing it in my city and decided to buy one for my friend for secret santa and they loves it
Extremely comfortable. Wears well, not too wide. But You’re forced to turn up the hat so much that it doesn’t look right, looks odd with so much folded up. Doesn’t need to be made so long.
This is a VERY large fit be warned, my husband is not a small guy and it is too large on him, I wouldn't be able to borrow this touque way to big that's for sure

This hat is really large and loose, and I personally prefer tight hats. By all means, my head is not small.

+1 star because it's warm
Great toque, got the black and it’s going to be perfect for Canadian Winter lol

Huge carhartt fan have thousands of dollars worth of their clothing , but this , i have a large head and its like xxxxxxxxL , not even funny theres a good 8 inches that just lose at the top. very disapointed.
I got the black beanie and it was way too long. A lot longer then what they show in the pictures.
I have a super size head and this hat fits nicely, lots of room at the top, good quality warm hat.

Awesome!
Bought for my husband who has a massive head. Fits his head. Good quality

review_title: Loved the "fat" flipped part of the beanie
reviews: Loved the "fat" flipped part of the beanie. It appears to be well made, with a medium-weight fabric that is also very stretchy. It's what I expected it to be. Has somewhat of a street wear look to it, but I can also see this worn as a normal toque. Will buy another in black and maybe some other colour.
Hat seems to be very durable and woven with a decent amount of quality. At the price point, there is really nothing to complain about.
Best hat a ever had. A bit too small but it eventually took my size

a trendy hat that fits all head shapes and sizes. my aunt had a hard time finding a hat that fit her just right and this was the also adding on that it’s a trend to wear these. amazing quality and price and recommend to all
I bought this item for work as I work outside, seems well made, fits well. No complaints.

review_title: But nevertheless its at a good price & does the job of keeping me cozy
reviews: I have an original & this definitely isn't the same Carhart if ya know what I mean. But nevertheless its at a good price & does the job of keeping me cozy. It sits a little tall on the top so pull the back down generally.
Perfect fit, warm around the ears, plenty of room for adjusting lengths, comfortable and matches all of my jackets. Very satisfied.
It goes on your head and keeps you relatively warm.
I got a big head so it’s a bit tighter than I thought it would be. Genuine carhartt quality item here though which I was worried of
fits well, seem like the real macoy. Keeps the head warm on cold days

i love this hat so much, its 100% authentic and very comfortable. it was also super fast delivery, only took about a day! i have nothing bad to say and i will definitely consider buying from them again:)

Love this hat, bought the Black one. Fits good and is higher quality material. Stitching looks great for a hat that I wore all winter and threw in the washing machine a few time. Overall 9/10 very nice
Parfait je recommande à 100% super maintien et garde au chaud
Warm and fits as expected. Just roll it up to get the fit you want.

review_title: Good product would buy it again definitely recommend it. Good price also.
reviews: Have always liked Carhart products and this was no lock down. Well-made fits good toasty warm.
Quality seems fine. Hat is longer than pictured. You gotta do some adjusting and playing around to make it for right, otherwise it looks real goofy.
Fits good, lots of stretch, keeps the head and ears warm
Exactly as pictured. Great quality. I basically live in it now. I’ll be buying it in the neon yellow colour soon!
Great bang for the buck. Stocking stuffer for my 14 year old son. Delivered within 24 hours. Amazon comes through once again!
Fit a bit tight but really warm. Love it
Purchased to wear working outside, and has become my favorite toque. So warm, and big enough to wear with a pony if I needed. Will buy in more colors.
It is a perfect, good quality carhartt hat but it does puff up a lot so if you want a touque that huge your head, this may not be the style of hat that you want.
It fits very well but it does stretch out very very fast which I was pretty upset about because when u was it even alone it starts to pill

review_title: a bit too big but its adjustable and very warm
reviews: a bit too big but its adjustable and very warm

It is a good hat for winter days. But I have not washed it yet. I will update this review after I wash this hat.
So far so good
Fits perfect. Very warm. Really good quality.
Carhartt quality. Great fit and nice and soft. Warm. Recommended
Fits great and is very warm. Never disappointed with Carthartt
I had my last hat for almost 3 years.. There built to last.. I do machine wash first time.. Then hand wash once amonth if that.. Good winter hat..
I should have bought Herschel... He doesn't wear it. :(
Just as expected! Love the quality
Buy only if your head and forehead combined are over 20 inches. This tuque is way too big. Still trying to figure out a way to wear and/or offer to someone with a major long face.
Pretty sure it’s a real brand toque. Fits perfect bought it for my boyfriend but he wears it a lot and looks a little worn already since Christmas. Wears it almost everyday
The hat fits great its warm. Very well made.

review_title: Great price and exactly as described
reviews: Exactly as pictured! Great price
holds shape, warm and great quality
Perfect size for my husband for Christmas.
Obsessed with this beanie, I have a big head and came fitting well and not too tight. It’s a longer style, so when it’s on there is extra room at the top as well. Going to purchase another
This toque is tiny, it must be a youth size, it barely fits my head and gives me headaches everytime I wear it! Wish I could exchange it but I've already worn it. So disappointed!!
all right

Fine for the price. But very VERY itchy, have worn acrylic toques most of my life, nothing like this. Ran it through the wash again to try and make it less itchy. Can't spend the winter with a red forehead, will be replacing.
